descriptionHtml:
Mod Name: Reaper's Witch of the Wild SevenBase MoreBounce TBBP.
By: Crazy1918 and AmevenAstral9


Description
===========
This is a conversion of the beautifull reaper's witch outfit standalone.

This mod add to the "leather" section of "Any Forge" 6 new items

- Witch of the Wild Horns (Circlet)
- Witch of the Wild Amulet
- Witch of the Wild Robe
- Witch of the Wild Bracers
- Witch of the Wild Ring
- Witch of the Wild Boots

Required mods
=============
None.

Credits
=======
Thanks to Reaper9111.

Sevennity-Demonhunter-crosscruasade and Wast1980 for the beautifull Body 'SevenBase Bombshell'.
